snippet.title: Hitchcock ni Chousen | Alfred Hitchcock Presents - 3DO Interactive Multiplayer Gameplay
snippet.description:
Released in 1993 exclusively in Japan, this 3DO game was developed and published by Toyota, a car manufacturer. (Yes, really!)

Dedicated to Alfred Hitchcock himself, this game contains a memory game and a roullete game. It's not a big game, but it is a rather interesting curiosity.
